title: Jerry Garcia -1995-04-28 - The Last Interview.mkv
description:
Jerry Garcia's Last Interview


On April 28, 1995, the Silicon Valley Historical Association filmed what turned out to be Jerry Garcia's final filmed interview.


Jerry talks about his early days as a musician, playing the blues for black audiences for food, LSD, living in his broken down Cadillac and some of the characters that helped him become a world-class musician and leader of the Grateful Dead.


Production Date: 2013
Playing Time: 53 Minutes
